attributes.Long form description:
The first instruction it's to assemble the chair.The student aligns the legs on a cross and proceeds to screws the center of the legs with the bolt, the wrench and the hex nut. The student rotates the legs and align the seat to the legs. Then screws the first leg and the instructor indicates that first it's needed to put the saddle washer.The student screws the 4 legs with the saddle washer. In the last step the student makes sure that the middle bolt
it's tighten.
